quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  114,1,"Say: “I seek refuge with the Lord of mankind"
  114,2,the Owner of mankind
  114,3,the real One worthy of worship of mankind
  114,4,from the evil of the sneaking whispers (Satan and its workers)
  114,5,who whispers into the hearts of people
  114,6,from (among) the jinns and mankind.”